###Block: Local Vars

LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|AllowedCharms			EXPLANATION:This determines how many charms are allowed on the item (Valid is 1 or 5)
LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|PossessedCharms		EXPLANATION:Counts how many Charms have been assigned to the item
LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|AllowedEssence		EXPLANATION:Determines how many 'Essence' are allowed on the item (Valid is 1 or 5)
LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|PossessedEssence		EXPLANATION:Counts how many Essence have been assigned to the item
LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|ItemLVL				EXPLANATION:Determines the level of a given item

