LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|LesserCharmBonus		EXPLANATION:Determines the Bonus for Lesser Charms
LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|GreaterCharmBonus		EXPLANATION:Determines the Bonus for Greater Charms
