LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|SpellEffectTierTwoTimes	EXPLANATION:Spell Effect EQMOD - Determines how many times the spell can be used in a single scene
LOCAL:EQUIPMENT|SpellEffectTierThreeTimes	EXPLANATION:Spell Effect EQMOD - Determines how many times the spell can be used in a single adventure
